    "name": "Smelogs Playground",
    "steam_appid": 1799530,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<strong>征服阿兹特克王国！</strong><br>Smelogs Playground邀请您进入古老阿兹特克文明的神秘世界。建造您的基地，指挥军队，施展强大的魔法咒语。无论您是经验丰富的战略家还是该类型的新手，Smelogs Playground提供了一个融合了战略、战斗和魔法的沉浸式体验。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >基地建造</h2>从零开始建造您的阿兹特克要塞。收集资源，建造洞穴系统，加固城墙。您将创建一座不可逾越的堡垒还是一个复杂的陷阱迷宫？您的基地是帝国的核心，其设计将影响您在战场上的成功。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1799530/extras/34dd62fca788acf67d855cf38ef93274.poster.avif?t=1733955146\" width=600 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1799530/extras/34dd62fca788acf67d855cf38ef93274.webm?t=1733955146\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1799530/extras/34dd62fca788acf67d855cf38ef93274.mp4?t=1733955146\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >动态侧升级</h2>在Smelogs Playground的神秘阿兹特克世界中，没有什么是静态的。单位拥有潜在的潜力——它们可以进化成建筑物，建筑物也可以重新变回战士。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1799530/extras/4edd5b817c99fdbd33f3c54027693d2b.poster.avif?t=1733955146\" width=600 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1799530/extras/4edd5b817c99fdbd33f3c54027693d2b.webm?t=1733955146\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1799530/extras/4edd5b817c99fdbd33f3c54027693d2b.mp4?t=1733955146\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >单位控制和战斗</h2>带领您的单位取得胜利。从迅速的球员到有力的战士再到强大的黑曜石炮，战略性地组建您的部队。在史诗般的战斗中微观管理部队，以击败敌人。见证军队的对决，他们争夺统治权。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1799530/extras/3aefabed2a6753d72bb132c9c5546003.poster.avif?t=1733955146\" width=600 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1799530/extras/3aefabed2a6753d72bb132c9c5546003.webm?t=1733955146\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1799530/extras/3aefabed2a6753d72bb132c9c5546003.mp4?t=1733955146\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >水晶法典咒语</h2>利用水晶法典的神秘能量。学习能够扭转战局的强大咒语。召唤彗星雨，治愈受伤的士兵和建筑物，或揭示隐藏的敌人。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1799530/extras/4bae31b51fe4d9903e20c9de5849cbd8.poster.avif?t=1733955146\" width=600 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1799530/extras/4bae31b51fe4d9903e20c9de5849cbd8.webm?t=1733955146\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1799530/extras/4bae31b51fe4d9903e20c9de5849cbd8.mp4?t=1733955146\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >基地编辑器</h2>定义比赛开始之前您的初始基地应该是什么样子的。您可以在比赛开始之前就为战略深度放置单位和建筑物。释放您的创造力！设计定制的基地，并与朋友分享。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1799530/extras/86ea8f995e4e91fc3d594f77fba7f912.poster.avif?t=1733955146\" width=600 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1799530/extras/86ea8f995e4e91fc3d594f77fba7f912.webm?t=1733955146\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1799530/extras/86ea8f995e4e91fc3d594f77fba7f912.mp4?t=1733955146\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >具有中立目标的程序生成地图</h2>航行，适应并克服未知的中立目标，并谨防未知的生物。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1799530/extras/b0436baeb2f43e39260ba2332195c5e2.poster.avif?t=1733955146\" width=600 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1799530/extras/b0436baeb2f43e39260ba2332195c5e2.webm?t=1733955146\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1799530/extras/b0436baeb2f43e39260ba2332195c5e2.mp4?t=1733955146\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >玩家进步和自定义</h2>通过级别并解锁新的挑战和装饰。<br>个性化您的外观、头像、边框和头衔。在战场上脱颖而出，让您的敌人知道他们正在对抗谁。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1799530/extras/573b365ccd48d269147e33af4cef7e73.poster.avif?t=1733955146\" width=600 height=198 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1799530/extras/573b365ccd48d269147e33af4cef7e73.webm?t=1733955146\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1799530/extras/573b365ccd48d269147e33af4cef7e73.mp4?t=1733955146\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >在线排名对战</h2>挑战最强者：与来自世界各地的玩家竞技。通过赢得战斗来攀登排名梯子。从新手到大师逐渐上升。<br>Elo积分：每次胜利都会赢得Elo积分，而失败则会扣除。证明您的战略能力，并上升至顶级排名。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >自定义游戏大厅</h2>主持您的竞技场：创建具有个性化规则的自定义游戏大厅。选择地图设置，甚至调整资源速率。邀请朋友或其他战略家加入您的私人比赛。<br>多样性释放：无论是无冲突的小规模战斗还是资源丰富的冲突，都可以根据您的喜好调整游戏。尝试非传统策略和设置。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >与人工智能的小规模战斗</h2>训练场：磨练您的技能。面对狡猾的人工智能对手。调整难度水平——从新手到神——并学习单位管理和基地建设的复杂性。<br>尝试并学习：尝试新的战术，探索科技树，并发现隐藏的协同作用。人工智能会适应，所以保持警惕！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >单人和合作</h2>完成动态任务，管理您的装备，并在战场上平衡风险以确保成功的撤离并进一步前进。<br><br><strong>阿兹特克王国等待您的指挥。您会建立联盟，主宰排名榜，还是揭示Smelogs Playground的神秘？</strong>",
